description: Multi purpose Zing Drawstring Pouch features color-keyed stretch lycra top hem that allows the drawstring to slide smoothly and cinch tightly. Can be used in a bag for extra padding, worn on a belt through the reinforced web loop, or clipped to a bag, strap or belt using the sewn-on plastic snap hook. Hem colors allow color-coded organizing. Small Drawstring Pouch
title: Zing 560-102 SPB1 Small Pouch (Black/Blue)
